&lt;li&gt;Define and enforce data, process, and governance standards so GTM data is reliable, auditable, and decision‑ready.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with Finance on revenue analytics, cohort performance, sales efficiency, and payback metrics to inform investment decisions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own territory mapping and routing plans, scaling the program for automated efficiency.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
